These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, lavender, green, yellow
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, doctor, analyst, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, jazz, soul
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, colonial, victorian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bolivar, siglo, vegafina
 1. the person who likes light-blue is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the doctor##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the bolivar-smoker and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the person who likes yellow is the fan of electronic##1
10. the cape-cod house is the person who likes lavender##1
11. the victorian house is the analyst##1
12. the lawyer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the lawyer##1
14. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the colonial house##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Color          | green | lavender    | light-blue      | yellow  |
| Job         | doctor  | lawyer    | photographer       | analyst     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | soul       | funk          | electronic |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| House         | ranch-style   | cape-cod   | colonial      | victorian    |
| Cigar     | oliveros        | bolivar        | vegafina    | siglo    |

