The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, architect, writer, software-developer
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, camping, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, scientific, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, rock, electronic
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, russian, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, roller, trike
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the russian is the fan of indie##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the software-developer##1
 6. the canadian is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the architect is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fan of rock##1
12. the engineer is between the person driving the roller and the writer##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
14. the dutch is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Game      | mah-jongg | billiard     | canasta        | snooker      |
