 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the fan of folk##1
12. the owner of the pony is the owner of the pony##1
13. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan of disco##1
14. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
15. the person watching family movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
