The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: davidoffd-games, bellflower, rose, azalea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, fantasy, sports
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, milk, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, snake, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, tennis, weightlifting
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff, chaman, bongani
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who growsbellflower and the davidoff-smoker##2
 3. the person watching crime movies is the person traveling to davidoffrot##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the ferret##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the person who growsdavidoffd-games is on the far right##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
12. the person who growsazalea is the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking milk##1
14. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
15. the person who's sport is badminton is the owner of the hedgehog##1
16. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person traveling to davidoffrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |    3     |      4      |
| City          | davidoffrot        | edinburgh | boston     | rome        |
| Flower         | azalea       | rose   | bellflower  | davidoffd-games  |
